===胸平面===
* '''胸平面'''（thoracic plane）是上下縱膈之間的分野。為以{{tsl|en|sternal angle|胸骨角}}為基準的{{tsl|en|anatomical plane|解剖平面}}，約在[[胸椎|胸椎]]T4-T5間的[[椎间盘|椎间盘]]<ref>[http://anatomy.med.umich.edu/cardiovascular_system/thorax_wall_ans.html Thoracic Wall, Pleura, and Pericardium - Dissector Answers<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120901215701/http://anatomy.med.umich.edu/cardiovascular_system/thorax_wall_ans.html |date=2012-09-01 }}</ref><ref>[http://dba.med.sc.edu/GROSS/practise1.htm Untitled Document<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://anatomy.uams.edu/AnatomyHTML/topogr_thorax.html |title=UAMS Department of Anatomy - Topographical Anatomy - Thorax<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2016-09-25 |archive-date=2004-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040817005148/http://anatomy.uams.edu/anatomyhtml/topogr_thorax.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

